      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests and manufactured solution benchmarks required for hemolysis-relevant flow regimes.",
      "rationale": "Vendor benchmark suite covers basic pipe flow and lid-driven cavity. No manufactured-solution verification for rotating machinery hemolysis regimes has been performed. Gap remains."
