      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) below 5% for NIH quantity of interest across all operating points.",
      "rationale": "GCI for the fine-to-medium mesh transition is 8.3%, exceeding the 5% threshold. Rotor tip clearance region drives residual discretization error. Achieved level 2."
