      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions must match VAD operating envelope including blood analog viscosity, temperature, and inlet boundary conditions.",
      "rationale": "In-vitro tests used porcine blood at 37 °C matching clinical conditions. Inlet velocity profiles were measured with LDV. Minor mismatch in hematocrit range (40–45% vs. 42% nominal) contributes to level gap."
