      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (e.g., E% or validation metric u_val) must be below defined tolerance for all 5 operating points.",
      "rationale": "Two of five operating points exceed the 35% relative error tolerance. No formal validation metric per ASME V&V 20 was applied. Achieved level 2."
