      "acceptanceCriteria": "Systematic evaluation of turbulence model form uncertainty and hemolysis constitutive law uncertainty required for MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected without comparative evaluation against RSM or LES. Power-law hemolysis model form uncertainty not quantified. Factor not assessed."
