      "acceptanceCriteria": "Full Monte Carlo propagation of all uncertain input parameters (viscosity, pump clearances, inlet profiles) through hemolysis prediction required.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was performed on viscosity and inlet velocity only. Geometric manufacturing tolerances on impeller clearances were not included. Partial UQ insufficient for MRL 5; factor not assessed."
